title: Inside Adam Savage's Cave: Gods of Egypt Stunt Weapons!
description:
It's like a late Christmas at Adam's cave as he opens of box of props from the film Gods of Egypt--part of a large collection of costumes and props on auction later this month. These stunt weapons stand up to scrutiny up close, and show the production designer's take on Egyptian mythology. 

Find out more about the props and costumes from Gods of Egypt here: https://propstore.com/gods-of-egypt-auction-preview-gallery/

Shot by Gunther Kirsch

Subscribe for more videos! http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=testedcom

Thanks for watching!
